      "side": 1,
      "message": "This follows the approach agreed with the Yosemite V5 team. The PDB is shared across platforms, while the MB and SCM are platform-specific. Therefore, only PDB-related FSC entries remain in the PDB config, and the other platform-specific entries, including those for MB sensors, are kept in the SCM config. This is consistent with the YV5 change https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/entity-manager/+/90794 .",
